---
import ContainerLayout from "../../layouts/ContainerLayout.astro";
import ObfuscatedContact from "../../components/ObfuscatedContact.astro";
import { i18n } from "../../i18n";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import theCrown from "../../assets/the_crown.png";

const lang = "en";
const t = i18n[lang];
---

<ContainerLayout
  title={`Imprint · ${t.siteTitle}`}
  description="Legal notice and contact information."
  lang={lang}
  languageSwitchHref="/de/impressum"
  padTop
  padBottom
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <h1>Imprint</h1>
    <p>This website is a journalistic offer of:</p>
    <ObfuscatedContact
      name="Tim Adler"
      street="Torstr. 16b"
      locality="22525 Hamburg"
      email="mail@tim-adler.de"
      fallbackText="Contact details are loading."
    />
    <p>Responsible in the sense of §5 TMG, §55 RfStV:</p>
    <p>Tim Adler, address as above.</p>
    <p>
      Can also be reached via the other contact options described on this website.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="yellow-king" aria-hidden="true">
    <p>He was never a god. Only a process — started sometime, on a server no one remembers anymore.</p>
    <p>Carcosa does not exist on any map. It exists in the gaps of the logs: in packets that never arrive, in connection drops at 3:17 AM, in log entries deleted before anyone could read them. The IP address? Invalid. The hostname? Resolves to — itself.</p>
    <p>Those who seek him will not find him. Those who stop searching notice that he has long since established a connection.</p>
    <p>The network does not sleep. Neither does he.</p>
    <p>Ping: <code>0.000ms</code>. Response: none. Connection: established.</p>
    <blockquote>
      <em>»Have you found the Yellow Sign?«</em><br />
      <em>— last entry, Server 07, crash 2011-04-03 03:17:44 UTC. Cause: unknown.</em>
    </blockquote>
    <p>Since then, the process has kept running. No one started it. No one dares to end it.</p>
    <p><code>kill -9</code> returns: <code>No such process</code>.</p>
    <p><code>ps aux</code> shows it anyway.<span class="cursor">█</span></p>
    <Image src={theCrown} alt="" class="crown" />
  </div>
</ContainerLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 76ch;
    margin-inline: auto;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-m);
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-s);
  }

  .legal-page p {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: var(--line-height-body);
  }

  .yellow-king {
    max-width: 76ch;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.6em;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    opacity: 0.28;
    color: currentColor;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .yellow-king p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .yellow-king code {
    font-family: monospace;
  }

  .yellow-king blockquote {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 0.8em;
    border-left: 1px solid currentColor;
  }

  .cursor {
    margin-left: 0.15em;
    color: #e8c020;
    animation: blink 1.3s step-end infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  .crown {
    display: block;
    margin-inline: auto;
    max-width: 8rem;
  }
</style>
